data.description: All are welcome but only one will be lucky enough to own this home at 1805 N. St. Rt. 721 Bradford Ohio. Located in Newton Township and Newton School district. This beauty sits on 1.5 acres and boasts 2419 sq ft. 4 bedrooms with one on the first floor. 2 full baths, 1 up and 1 down. The kitchen was updated with bar area, cabinets galore and granite countertops. You will love the Genn-air cook-top and range hood added in 2015. Bosch dishwasher in 2017, sliding door in 2018, Trane furnace new in 2015, insulation was added in attic and garage in 2019, 1st floor shower in 2015, new well pump and sump pump in 2022. Outside you will enjoy the large front porch and the covered patio in back and if that's not enough there is an awesome 36x30 insulated barn with concrete floor and some new lighting. Sellers have never used the fireplace/not warranted. Full tank of propane will have to be worked out with buyer and seller.
